UrduDescription": null, "English": "Will, therefore, O Lord, my confession to You of the evils I have committed avail me anything? Will my admission to You of wrongs I have done deliver me from the Wrath? Or, have You, in this, my situation, irrevocably decreed Your wrath for me? Does, in the time of praying, Your displeasure, inseparably cling to me?", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "یَااِلٰھِیْ اِقْرَارِیْ عِنْدَکَ بِسُوْٓئِ مَااَکْتَسَبْتُ وَھَلْ یُنْجِیْنِیْ مِنْکَ اِعْتَرَافِیْ لَکَ بِقَبِیْحِ مَااَرْتَکَبْتُ اَمْ اَوْجَبْتَ لِیْ فِیْ مَقَامِیْ ھٰذَاسُخْطَکَ اَمْ لَزِمَنِیْ فِیْ وَقْتِ دُعَآئِیْ مَقْتُکَ سُبْحَانَکَ لَااَیْئَسُ مِنْکَ وَقَدْ فَتَحْتَ لِیْ بَابَ التَّوْبَۃِ اِلَیْکَ بَلْ اَقُوْلُ مَقَالَ الْعَبْدِالذَّلِیْلِ الظَّالِمِ لِنَفْسِہِ الْمُسْتَخِفِّ بِحُرْمَۃِ رَبِّہِ الَّذِیْ عَظُمَتْ ذُنُوْبُہٗ فَجَلَّتْ وَاَدْبَرَتْ اَیَّامُہٗ فَوَلَّتْ حَتّٰی اِذَارَاٰی مُدَّۃَ الْعَمَلِ قَدِانْقَضَتْ وَغَایَۃَ الْعُمْرِ قَدْاِنْتَھَتْ وَاَیْقَنَ اَنَّہٗ لَا مَحِیْصَ لَہٗ مِنْکَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign