ou saying: O most merciful. O most compassionate of those to whom seekers after mercy continually come. O most Gracious of those whom seekers after pardon approach. O You whose forgiveness is more frequent than Your chastisement. O You Whose Approbation is more abundant than Your wrath. O You who favored Your creatures by overlooking their guilt.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَمَا اَنَا بِاَعْصٰی مَنْ عَصَاکَ فَغَفَرْتَ لَہٗ وَمَا اَنَا بِاَلْوَمَ مَنِ اعْتَذَرَ اِلَیْکَ فَقَبِلْتَ مِنْہُ وَمَا اَنَا بِاَظْلَمَ مَنْ تَابَ اِلَیْکَ فَعُدْتَ عَلَیْہِ اَتُوْبُ اِلَیْکَ فِیْ مَقَامِیْ ھٰذَا تَوْبَۃَ نَادِمٍ عَلٰی مَا فَرَطَ مِنْہُ مُشْفِقٍ مِّمَّا اِجْتَمَعَ عَلَیْہِ خَالِصَ الْحَیَآئِ مِمَّا وَقَعَ فِیْہِ عَالِمٍۢ بِاَنَّ الْعَفْوَ عَنِ الذَّنْۢبِ الْعَظِیْمِ لَا یَتَعَاظَمُکَ وَاَنَّ التَّجَاوُزَعَنِ الْاِثْمِ الْجَلِیْلِ لَا یَسْتَصْعِبُکَ وَاَنَّ اِحْتِمَالَ الْجِنَایَاتِ الْفَاحِشَۃِ لَایَتَکَادُکَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": 